{"id":66198,"type":4,"name":"The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d4/31/66198_vgcwp.jpg","rating":{"total":1334,"count":{"1":3,"2":1,"3":2,"4":2,"5":7,"6":34,"7":102,"8":337,"9":498,"10":348},"score":8.7},"summary":"《巫师3：狂猎》（波兰语：Wiedźmin 3: Dziki Gon，英语：The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt）是一款由波兰游戏工作室CD Projekt RED开发并发行的开放世界动作角色扮演游戏，于2013年2月公布。游戏于2015年5月19日在Microsoft Windows、PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台发布，这也是首款在PlayStation平台发布的巫师系列游戏。本作是巫师系列的第三部作品，同样改编自波兰奇幻小说作家安杰·萨普科夫斯基的同名系列小说（中译《猎魔人》），但剧情发生在小说之后。\r\n\r\n游戏以第三人称视角进行，玩家将继续扮演狩魔猎人利维亚的杰洛特，用剑和魔法来抵御在奇幻世界中遇到的危险，同时与非玩家角色进行互动，完成故事的主线与支线任务以推动剧情发展。玩家大多是徒步旅行，偶尔骑杰洛特的马“Roach”。\r\n\r\n本作在商业上取得成功并受到了广泛的赞誉，游戏在六周内销量超过600万。此游戏亦获得2015年游戏大奖的最佳年度游戏，以及最佳角色扮演游戏。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>巫师3：狂猎</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/20660\">CD Projekt</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/20660\">CD Projekt</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/34637\">Andrzej Sapkowski</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>猎魔人3：狂猎</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>巫师3：鬼猎</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>The Witcher 3 Wild Hunt</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Wiedzmin 3: Dziki Gon</li><li><span>平台: </span>Xbox Series X</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS5</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox One</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ARPG</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>REDengine3</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2015年5月19日</li><li><span>售价: </span>$59,99 / 127元</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://thewitcher.com/zh-cn/witcher3</li><li><span>总监: </span>Konrad Tomaszkiewicz、Mateusz Kanik、Sebastian Stępień</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span>Grzegorz Mocarski</li><li><span>制作人: </span>Piotr Krzywonosiuk、Jędrzej Mróz</li><li><span>剧本: </span>Marcin Blacha、Mateusz Tomaszkiewicz</li><li><span>美工: </span>Marian Chomiak</li><li><span>音乐: </span>Marcin Przybylowicz、Mikolai Stroinski</li><li><span>摄影: </span>Robert Stoneman</li><li><span>配音导演: </span>Damien Goodwin、Michal Konarski、Kate Saxon</li><li><span>其他发行日期: </span>2016年8月(年度版)</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">其他发行日期: </span>2019年10月15日(NS)</li>","collection":{"wish":304,"collect":1287,"doing":386,"on_hold":256,"dropped":64},"tags":[{"name":"RPG","count":328},{"name":"PC","count":227},{"name":"我们来盘昆特牌吧","count":203},{"name":"CD_Projekt_RED","count":197},{"name":"PS4","count":159},{"name":"ARPG","count":149},{"name":"The_Witcher","count":117},{"name":"昆特牌","count":112},{"name":"欧美系","count":75},{"name":"STEAM","count":69},{"name":"2015","count":51},{"name":"波兰","count":45},{"name":"XboxOne","count":11},{"name":"开放世界","count":9},{"name":"CDPR","count":7},{"name":"ACT","count":6},{"name":"神作","count":6},{"name":"奇幻","count":5},{"name":"Switch","count":4},{"name":"巨乳","count":4},{"name":"巫师","count":4},{"name":"波兰蠢驴","count":3},{"name":"繁体中文版","count":3},{"name":"烧鸡狂魔","count":3},{"name":"沙盒","count":3},{"name":"单机","count":3},{"name":"NS","count":2},{"name":"索尼大法好","count":2},{"name":"游戏","count":2},{"name":"CDProjektRED","count":2}],"crt":[{"id":25981,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e9/83/25981_crt_5MX7z.jpg","name":"利维亚的杰洛特","desc":"山路和弘"},{"id":42731,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/20/2f/42731_crt_qTwdq.jpg","name":"希瑞菈","desc":"沢城みゆき"},{"id":54087,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/47/47/54087_crt_JJARn.jpg","name":"温格堡的叶妮芙","desc":"田中敦子"},{"id":55019,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/17/62/55019_crt_RSY9d.jpg","name":"西吉斯蒙德·迪科斯徹","desc":"ふくまつ進紗"},{"id":54088,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3c/36/54088_crt_a2FaQ.jpg","name":"特莉丝·梅利葛德","desc":"逢沢ゆりか"},{"id":54091,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/88/8b/54091_crt_FwBRb.jpg","name":"艾瑞汀·布里克·格拉斯","desc":"秋元羊介"},{"id":54974,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8c/2b/54974_crt_6Jsco.jpg","name":"恩希尔·恩瑞斯","desc":"